---
title: Cranberry Dijon Turkey Meatloaves plus a Brussels Sprout, Sweet Potato & Toasted Almond Jumble
description: Sure, your grandma’s meatloaves have a lot of love in them. But that same-old, same-old recipe could use a twist once in a while, no? Our chefs nailed it with this update on the home-cooked favorite, swapping beef and pork for turkey mixed with zesty Fry Seasoning. Ketchup stayed in the back of the fridge in favor of a Dijon mustard and cranberry jam glaze, and sad steamed broccoli turned into a jubilee of roasted veggies. We’re pretty sure this meal would even wow Grandma.
